# INFRA CLEAN CLOUD - MARKETING SITE RULES
# Version: 1.2.0 | Last Updated: March 25, 2026

## REQUIRED READS (MARKETING)
1. MARKETING_COPY_GUIDE.md - Palantir-style copy and structure
2. README.md - Local development and structure

## DEPLOYMENT — MANDATORY PROCESS
# ⛔ NEVER DEPLOY DIRECTLY TO PRODUCTION
# ALWAYS: local validate → UAT preview → present results → get operator approval → then prod
# SEE .cursor/rules/deployment-guardrails.mdc FOR FULL PROCESS
# VIOLATION OF THIS PROCESS IS NOT ACCEPTABLE

## COPY GUARDRAILS
- Follow Palantir-style tone: executive, outcomes-first, evidence-led
- Maintain section integrity (framing, operating model, proof, CTA)
- Avoid casual language or feature-first copy
- Ensure every page supports executive decision-making

## DESIGN GUARDRAILS
- Respect existing layout, spacing, and color palette
- Preserve typography and tone
